title: The Gettysburg Story - Battlefield Auto Tour
description:
This is a complete rip (at 320kbps using LAME) of The Gettysburg Story: Battlefield Auto Tour.  The retail version of this will run you about $30, and it includes a nice pamphlet of extra information about the Battle.  The pamphlet includes the map of the tour route, but you can just go to this site for a PDF of it: http://www.nps.gov/gett/planyourvisit/upload/GETT%20brochure.pdf

I found the tour to be very interesting, and it is well worth your time!

I hope you enjoy it and learn a lot! If you can, please support the town of Gettysburg and the preservation of the Battlefields.


I'll be seeding this from my laptop that isn't always on, so just sit tight for a bit and I'll make sure to get it to you as soon as I can :)
